 | date= 2007-11-12
 | accessdate=2009-04-22}}
</ref> In April 2009, Albania and Croatia announced a plan to jointly construct a 1,500&nbsp;MWe nuclear power plant on the shores of [[Lake Scutari]] (Lake Shkodër), near Albania's border with [[Montenegro]].<ref name="albania2">
